Draft prj user manual (1)
=========================

Goal
-----

Create a first draft of the **prj** tool user manual.
The user manual shall act as the primary high level specification of the **prj** tool.
This first draft should include enough detail to support the first iteration of development of the **prj** tool.
The first development iteration will be used to support development of other product components.

The first draft is not exepcted to be complete, and should be reviewed on this basis.


Completion
-----------

Draft version completed, and reviewed by changhua and stg.
Merging to development tree based on these reviews.
